title: Wilson Lane
description: A contemporary residential project showcasing modern architectural elements with clean lines and sustainable design. The home features innovative interior spaces that blur the boundaries between indoor and outdoor living.

title: Springvale Road
description: An elegant residential renovation that combines traditional charm with modern functionality. The design emphasizes natural light and open floor plans while respecting the neighborhood's historic character.

title: Watermill Lane
description: A sophisticated residential design that integrates seamlessly with its natural surroundings. The project features custom millwork and thoughtful material selections that create warm, inviting living spaces.

title: Wapakoneta Road
description: A striking contemporary home that maximizes views and natural light through strategic window placement and open-concept design. The architecture celebrates both privacy and connection to the landscape.

title: Wolf Run
description: A minimalist residential project that emphasizes simplicity and functionality. The design features clean geometric forms and carefully curated spaces that create a serene living environment.

title: Kiawah
description: An oceanfront residence that captures breathtaking coastal views while providing sophisticated indoor-outdoor living spaces. The design features elevated walkways, pool terraces, and a distinctive helical stair tower.

title: Kiwi Meditation Cabin
description: A competition entry for a small meditation retreat that harmonizes with its natural environment. The design explores minimal intervention architecture with sustainable materials and contemplative spatial experiences.

title: Metsa Library
description: A conceptual library design that integrates learning spaces with landscape architecture. The proposal emphasizes natural light, flexible study environments, and community gathering spaces within a forest setting.
